dct_title_s: Antarctica, Porpoise Bay to West Ice Shelf (Raster Image)
dct_description_sm: Prepared and published by the Defense Mapping Agency. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. "From various sources to 1961." This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA).
